  "description": "Details of Condition 6 'Hard and Soft Landscaping', Condition 7 'Site Boundaries', Condition 8 'Cycle Storage', Condition 9 'External Facing Materials' and Condition 11 'Detailed Drawings' as required by planning application LBS reg No 19/AP/1375 - Retention refurbishment of the existing front main part of the building except its main roof. Removal of all rear parts and main roof of the existing building. Erections of 3-storey rear extension and mansard style roof extension to the existing building. Rationalise, deepen and extend the existing basement area. Change of use of the basement in the main building from storage to commercial (B1) unit of 130m2 and first floor offices to residential (C3). Reduction of existing ground floor offices from 110m2 to 74m2. Provision of five residential units (comprising 3 x 2B4P and 2 studio flats) in proposed first, second and third floor with associated amenity space and separate cycle and bin storage area for both residential and commercial units. Installation of 8 solar panels on main roof top of the building.",
